---
title: Homemade Cheesy Chorizo and Bean Jacky-P with Charred Corn Slaw
description: Jacket potatoes aren't just for baked beans and cheese... unless they are! Make your own beans to pile on top of a humble jacket potato for a comforting weeknight dinner.
